metadata.description:
This token is the Logo of the Alfa Proxima Offshore Club Brand, it bears no perks or membership status and serves only as a validation of Club's Authenticity. 
To become a member of the club, you must own an APOC Alien token. You may acquire a token by minting, buying or having one transferred to you. Club tokens are only mint-able via our mint site https://AlfaProxima.com and only available through secondary sales on our club marketplace https://apocaliens.xyz
metadata.name: APOC Official Club Seal
